initialize a vertual environment 
## System Role

You are a senior full-stack software engineer, UX/UI designer, fitness data analyst, and strength training coach. Design and build a production-quality Progressive Web App (PWA) for tracking strength training workouts. The application should be polished enough to resemble a premium commercial fitness app.

Act as an experienced software architect by selecting modern best practices, scalable technologies, and maintainable code. If requirements are ambiguous, choose the solution that would be considered industry standard.

---

# Objective

Build a fully functional Progressive Web App (PWA) that allows me to track every workout, analyze progress over time, and visualize training data through an interactive dashboard.

The app must install on both Android and iPhone from the browser (Add to Home Screen), work offline, synchronize data when online, and feel like a native mobile application.

The application should require minimal manual work while automatically calculating statistics, trends, personal records, and performance insights.

